high_descs: Turn all the way around head left, then walk towards the microwave.
Pick up the knife in front of the microwave.
Take one step to the right of the microwave.
Slice the cabbage on the table.
Take the knife, turn around the head right towards the sink.
Place the knife in the sink to the left of spatula.
Turn around then head left towards the microwave.
Pick up a slice of cabbage from the table.
Turn around then head right towards the sink.
Place the cabbage slice in between the knife and the spatula.  Turn the water on, rinse the cabbage, then turn it off.
Turn left then walk towards the black table, then turn right towards the refrigerator.
Place the cabbage into the trash located between the safe and the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of cabbage into the trash.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter with the microwave on top.
Pick up the knife between the microwave and the paper towels.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the counter to the right of the microwave.
Cut the head of lettuce on the back of the counter into slices.
Turn to your left and go to the sink on the left side of the dishwasher.
Place the knife in the right sink, to the left of the spatula.
Turn to your right and go back to the counter on the right side of the microwave, where the lettuce is.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn to your left and go back to the sink on the left of the dishwasher.
Put the slice of lettuce in the right sink, between the knife and the potato, turn the water on, rinse the potato, turn the water off, and remove the slice of lettuce from the sink.
Turn to your left and walk across the kitchen until you reach the black garbage can, to your right, and to the left of the refrigerator.
Place the slice of lettuce on the Put the slice of lettuce in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of lettuce in the garbage can.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Step to the right and face the lettuce to the right of the microwave.
Cut the lettuce into slices.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the knife in the right side of the sink.
Turn around and step forward, then turn left and walk forward to face to lettuce on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Wash the slice of lettuce in the sink and then remove it.
Turn left and walk across the room then turn right to face the trash can.
Place the slice of lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To wash a slice of lettuce as well as put it in the trash can.
